{"tid":594512,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解講「抵死」 就係冷血","createTime":"2018-03-16T01:29:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-19T01:23:45.000Z","uid":2719,"like":38,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"fc5e0ce5ce90dc81dc4932be1050e0a25f2e0e90","tid":594512,"uid":2719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T01:29:35.000Z","msg":"如果事件嘅因係自作孽<br />\n例如廢老亂過馬路俾車撞死<br />\n伴侶不忠引起爭執造成傷忙等<br />\n點解唔可以話抵死<br />\n<br />\n如果事件嘅因唔關事主事<br />\n例如天災 先天性疾病 其它意外等<br />\n個意外同人嘅行為無直接關係 先值得憐憫<br />\n<br />\n但我見好多時自作孽post<br />\n有人講世人所謂嘅風涼話<br />\n就俾人瘋狂負評<br />\n明明係抵死 有乜好rip乜乜柒柒<br />\n<br />\n就我個人立場<br />\n港女俾mk殺<br />\n<br />\nMk 殺人一定係錯<br />\n港女一定係受害者<br />\n不過凡事都有因果<br />\n導火線係條友惹岀嚟<br />\n所以佢都要承受各可能嘅風險<br />\n<br />\n所以 受害者 都有分抵死唔抵死<br />\n就咁講個港女係受害者<br />\n有無辜嘅意思 即係我第二段講嘅情況<br />\n個港女明顯係第一段 所以係「抵死」<br />\n<br />\n係抵死嘅受害者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9be9054f74e6fab5d397bcdebe8ef254b9299318","tid":594512,"uid":21423,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T01:31:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f9067ae4b921649eb4d01fccb059639b44ec02d3","tid":594512,"uid":138197,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T01:33:46.000Z","msg":"抵啦"},{"pid":"db4a161dcd66fbf26cc5f84f1c6a42fc4ade7370","tid":594512,"uid":2772,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T01:35:24.000Z","msg":"聽講佢用微信<br />\n所以我覺得係抵死既"},{"pid":"4ee1b64a9c0081c2eb7a69d25b2518bf6f66814f","tid":594512,"uid":2719,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"9be9054f74e6fab5d397bcdebe8ef254b9299318","tid":594512,"uid":21423,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T01:31:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-03-16T01:36:42.000Z","msg":"捉唔到錯字?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69fa920524e33a74f3297e24da4fd54aa05ad8ab","tid":594512,"uid":57513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018